  Stable for x86, wrt bug #535110

  17 Jan 2015; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> libcgroup-0.41.ebuild:
  Stable for ppc, wrt bug #535110

  09 Jan 2015; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> libcgroup-0.41.ebuild:
  Stable for amd64, wrt bug #535110

  18 Nov 2014; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> libcgroup-0.41.ebuild:
  Fix SRC_URI, remove unused version mangling.

  17 Nov 2014; Markos Chandras <hwoarang@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  Dropping to maintainer-needed since Andreis hasn't been maintaining it for
  quite a while

  17 Nov 2014; Markos Chandras <hwoarang@gentoo.org> files/cgconfig.initd:
  Fix default group detection by vinz meier. Bug #510802

